snippet.title: Silvarret
snippet.description:
Here you'll find theme park building with an eye for amusement design, city building with a knack for urbanism and building... building with attention to detail. I've been an active member of simulation gaming communities for many years, I have an MA degree in Urban Studies, and I've travelled around the world to ride the best roller coasters - now I'm just sharing my creations on YouTube and hopefully teaching people some things along the way.

I always read comments, but reach out to me on Twitter if you really want to talk about something! You can also reach me at silvarret@gmail.com!
